content.rendered:
Directed by Raj Mehta

Written by Sumit Batheja. Rishhabh Sharrma. Rishhabh Sharrma. Anurag Singh. Anurag Singh. Neeraj Udhwani

Star Varun Dhawan(Kukoo Saini). Anil Kapoor(Bheem Saini). Kiara Advani(Naina Sharma). Neetu Singh(Geeta Saini). Prajakta Koli(Ginny Saini). Manish Paul(Gurpreet Sharma). Tisca Chopra(Meera). Savant Singh Premi(Balwinder). Manmeet Singh Sawhney(Dr. Bhatia (as Manmeet Singh)). Shivangi Singh(Rimpy). Varun Sood(Gaurav). Elnaaz Norouzi(Russian Party Girl). Balwinder Begowal(Guru Maa). Suparna Marwah(Sushma – Naina’s Mother). Deepak Kripalani(Anil – Naina’s Father). Sanchit Chanana(Kid Kukoo). Shivika(Kid Naina). Veer(School Kid – Kukoo’s Friend). Viren(School Kid – Sonu). Shivani Sopori(Aunty #1). Mridula Oberoi(Aunty #2). Naman Arora(Vishal – The Feminine Guy). Akshay Datta(Kukoo’s Pub Colleague). Sunil Rodrigues(Giant Sardar at Gurpreet’s Office). Mohit Sharma(Gogi). Gagandeep(Bittu). Anuj(Veera). Manoj Dutt(Family Court Judge). Paramjeet Singh(Family Lawyer). Somnath Chakravarty(Family Court Clerk). Rahul Saxena(Male House Help). Pooja(Female House Help). Alok Nath Pathak(Pandit at Remarriage). Atul Desai(Tailor at Showroom). Denis Kot(Naina’s EA). Richard Lee(Jeff Morgan). Fernando Moreno(Guy at the Pub). Tanya(Waitress at the Pub). Anna Zolotukhina(Drunk Girl at the Pub). Stanislav Nazirov(Homeless Man in Toronto). Karan Puri(Balwinder’s Drunk Friend). Kailash Topnani(Kukoo’s Friend). Sanket Ranadive(School Band Lead Singer). Varinder(PT Teacher). Sumeet Verma(Harbhajan – Bheem’s Driver)

Language Hindi

Producers Alex Anthony Fernandes. Hiroo Johar. Karan Johar. Madhav Roy Kapur. Satish Mane. Apoorva Mehta. Dmitriy D. Zaytsev

Production Dharma Productions. Viacom18 Motion Pictures
